WELCOME TO

 

OUR FAMILY

We would like to welcome you to Anemos Greek Cuisine. We are a Greek restaurant in Manalapan, NJ. We are dedicated to both serving authentic Greek food while transporting you to Greece when you walk through our doors. Anemos is a term derived from the Greek word, νεμος, meaning wind. Our restaurant has an authentic, cozy, Mediterranean atmosphere infused in the aromas of delicious Greek and Mediterranean delights.

 

Anemos Greek Cuisine is the perfect place for lunch, dinner, private parties, and your catering needs. We serve the freshest Greek and Mediterranean dishes in Central New Jersey. Come and experience the traditional taste of our Greek cuisine.
